  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8cf36fa1-9436-447a-9057-2202175f1e03\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224308480481/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ade63d90-4a13-4e92-8ca1-f3157bf1da03\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f8e7c34b-b5ee-4ee3-b8f0-d923ee6b2cdd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a1ee2cf-52dc-4095-ac26-a2f9df125063\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요. (주)파파스컴퍼니입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-655aea70-a97a-4ad0-a4c9-3a19f2ef3b2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b5fb3a81-7c3b-4c1e-b236-01341abab782\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-438bb684-1e41-4cfe-a70b-642aa716447e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aca885df-c496-4239-916f-907891cc0d30\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 소량 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-44017348-a654-4f97-bdbf-49bb9306f1e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>롤스티커</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61ea7394-c6bb-49a5-9785-2ddaf5eb6885\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에 대해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ddf85868-3bfe-40ab-9505-4f488556973c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-264e7b13-ffb1-4a8e-ae60-4616c1f091c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다시 한번 확인해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-316a9a2f-40e6-4b25-9058-8caeacc5a90c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b88ff553-6b0a-4895-9876-706deef42b26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f1a08f8a-74d5-421b-bfa6-0621c3a274d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a1186030-167d-462b-bf43-9d21735a150b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c4951c34-aa64-4e41-ada5-92bbafc9a80f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c3f1a81-f89b-4e2d-bf4d-e628c0efe8ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7db4de51-e2f3-447e-8c4f-612e1b7dbb0c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ed74478f-e087-4089-88fc-1ecd3695519a\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">□ 롤스티커를 주로 사용하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc17bc5f-2226-4581-bf47-2b1a7ca25c02\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0180dc7a-80e2-4248-b35d-7438537bf46d\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">업체(산업군) 및 기업 추천</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-76e14484-a742-4859-af2e-4ba627e638e6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4defde79-6b15-4598-a547-333783e55d01\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5998c03d-a01a-46cb-b543-19e2a51a4e4c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-590daf3d-a0bf-4358-95ef-128060979252\" style=\"color:#555555;\">롤스티커는 \"규격화된 용기\"에 \"대량으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5da51272-5def-4eb6-99ff-0149cb0158c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81659c31-cfc7-47b0-a9f1-9771eb9b0fec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자동 부착\"해야 하는 산업군에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-43cf6f95-62f7-45fc-87c7-ce10775a6793\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9919111-1485-4a39-bea5-a5a3ee7e451e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">필수적으로 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bca96fcd-d789-4fa4-a611-32b340b067fa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-800a9ad8-74e9-46ed-a587-1cb3ba7e20f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사람이 손으로 붙이기 불가능한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8c02e2cb-ea12-44c6-a44c-0d06377a53cc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25c90267-abb8-4a2e-be93-e61a06dd1d57\" style=\"color:#555555;\">생산 속도를 감당해야 하기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-792aa9bb-6cf4-4999-871f-914db349c31c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f759e779-d755-4f88-8570-8be8e7969a00\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대표적인 3대 산업군과 해당 분야의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c69ab8cd-b0e0-468f-90e3-385b44366934\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b9c0eb49-c066-4720-94db-8bc0a06b5661\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상징적인 기업들을 소개합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a0077648-5ed2-46aa-9c18-368aa69a0b82\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-45daab2b-df15-4058-8ad8-72b72cc3c0d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c34f1e93-411e-46d8-8505-9cbc66318a7c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4e6f9dd-6604-442c-afee-f223b6dd9502\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">① 화장품 제조 및 브랜드사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e56fff41-b718-4977-8d9f-645ec4f16040\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ce46a87-3348-407d-bea8-4266a3af91bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">화장품은 스킨, 로션, 크림 등 원통형이나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-276bcdb4-e0cd-4f3d-a5d6-7477b97dcef2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4661f817-1fa0-46cb-b7f1-15445faa892b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사각형 모양의 용기가 매일 수만 ~ 수십만 개씩</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b031d345-275d-47ba-8e10-ee50dbb3fbf7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f5d7bd07-f1fc-4183-a91a-3a4352538f06\" style=\"color:#555555;\">생산 라인을 통과합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0a649e59-576d-43c8-9c3b-874bd1fa59d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d62f6e7a-4be5-491d-b4f7-31cab8020424\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내용물의 특성에 따라 물이나 오일에 강한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b7c2041d-671a-43de-83ad-b9dc54f6dbcc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-47a1eb2f-9c81-48d0-b383-fb8684d35073\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'유포지'나 용기 본연의 색을 살리는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-949a3376-49b8-4440-a4d7-5086dc6983ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-441b2cad-3ab1-4f11-9a51-e0b4ecd25cc5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'투명 PET' 재질의 롤스티커를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e54bcb59-add1-423b-b4cb-a0034f22fd38\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecf2cef9-7b0a-49d4-be29-8530e96e5611\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자동 라벨러로 초고속 부착합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-29499b6b-02b8-4612-9830-efe10f4b24d1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-250c4197-1a2f-4def-b116-378eebfc3cb3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e7e1b817-d3a9-4afc-8186-7bd9f85f6d82\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31419b08-736f-4e35-9554-4b2f7fefd9a3\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">② 식품 및 음료 제조사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c488b034-b251-4df0-8900-f57dc9c9ba5d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9eb73bf1-ee4f-4a19-b7de-7bbbda34f664\" style=\"color:#555555;\">참기름 병, 소스 용기, HMR(가정간편식)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-79bd5db1-a1cf-4b2b-b312-3639f8665897\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b671c97-cad3-4045-8693-1b299326b650\" style=\"color:#555555;\">밀키트 용기 등 식품업계는 롤스티커의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0607397f-36aa-4594-8c79-fbd298fd9940\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-79a2fc92-5a30-4057-ae77-8e492add8b1a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">최대 소비처 중 하나입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b15b2ba-4569-4ce4-99be-4021a7d910a0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c03b8d2b-9373-47e5-b300-b8f7f9ece5ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">식품 라벨은 냉장·냉동고의 습기를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e16af4fa-235f-41ef-bd5c-dce8f46b1714\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29e8421c-dcdf-4518-bdbd-c40dc6105741\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견뎌야 하므로 내수성이 강한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-00b25edc-b53b-4959-9b56-4af5e56a7f3b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f9255fc6-3aee-452e-859a-f078e07fa0fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특수 원단으로 만든 롤라벨을 부착기 기계로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-46966bc4-7091-449b-8620-cc289f50edff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ed549767-2807-4784-9310-eb3beb5366d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쉴 새 없이 찍어냅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2a5ff355-e660-4a14-bb44-597970fa854a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58b3a641-27c9-4f5b-949d-75d35a5ba91c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-153c3b56-98b7-4fbd-8cd8-1448c437af0a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ed15e8f1-dd93-4efc-9cd0-0b878839e361\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">③ 초대형 이커머스 및 물류·유통사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9d74b465-98a5-4998-b6d2-564b6b0ad4ee\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fe9bc480-62ca-46db-ae0e-a7f948316551\" style=\"color:#555555;\">화려한 제품 라벨 외에도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1c4fa6f4-4b16-4036-9cdd-7299a6288c00\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8821e49-32ac-4e1f-958a-0d18120032e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'물류용 바코드 스티커' 역시 엄청난 양의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1ca64c47-1099-4f5d-84ce-3741d48f6597\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7ae7998-4ff4-4435-904d-ad5abe34e551\" style=\"color:#555555;\">롤스티커를 소비합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5fc956e1-fbfe-416e-b3fd-46b1a2ae1ada\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6dff0cdf-4172-492f-ad13-3caa85e6ce3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수많은 택배 박스와 송장, 분류용 라벨은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-068e6b9b-dc43-410b-a2dd-223b17b8d76c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86c5d22d-9014-4e29-b7db-0e58048cca71\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사람이 손으로 붙일 수 없기 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5f3cf7f0-1077-4fe1-a47e-b29aef858971\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6cc0a6a-1f2c-4fc5-ba45-75bd114503cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">롤 형태로 감긴 감열지나 유포지를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-38ad5ba9-d1b1-45f1-a35a-e4b05d63dd5d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ad65bf0b-d8b8-4d85-b973-7d3c4eabb2a0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자동 인쇄·부착 시스템(Print &amp; Apply)에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7178e26a-de53-4209-bfa4-8f8da92e6a5d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53f02a16-3db9-40a3-978a-2161d2546221\" style=\"color:#555555;\">걸어 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e941fa50-d4ad-4767-be02-62810b758222\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2b43db8-40f9-4959-b6b2-b1cb64110d31\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8f5e616f-4e8d-4b01-a669-a3674fa42b5a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-16d5a66f-b48e-464f-989b-5a137b8fbebe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대량 생산 라인을 가진 대기업들이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c3de2f6a-825e-4823-84e0-78bb9133d461\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f250fda2-1262-4ec5-a821-bab986f6712c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수만, 수십만 장의 롤스티커를 자동 기계로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2dd0dd58-fe1c-4737-ba31-b29194187368\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-72e210c7-992e-4165-94a5-ba2199469a84\" style=\"color:#555555;\">찍어낸다면, '</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9b722a5-e96a-41af-b196-9ab5cc061de0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d663f39-0de7-4a1f-9b8f-ad0e86faee85\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'과 같은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c849c2ac-bbfb-4f33-8add-b24d0f897925\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-14be31fd-df64-40ee-b365-1f8c5d909b46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">감각적인 소규모 인쇄·디자인 에이전시가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1812b596-2fd8-4f2e-9fd7-17d4a2f401c3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-382477bb-ac63-458a-838e-8c67057d5bcc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">독점할 수 있는 고부가가치 타깃 시장은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-afbf16e1-4ae8-4fd5-a403-12fb6ce01a03\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ad641f77-f4ad-446f-b539-2f0ea48355ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">분명히 따로 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-aa141b75-b802-49b8-9f9b-8fba14c7cf14\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4997d7e0-14f8-4cab-a06f-f211dfd4d477\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2516d7a5-3b31-4782-9609-6b557827681c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5f2396ff-1689-4dcb-9270-11fb7caba7a7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">바로 기성 제품(Ready-made)으로는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5551f1db-e5a7-485c-b540-dd1e72ac35a0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa9f93c5-775a-4b70-a2c8-1f33363c9eaa\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">흉내 내기 힘든 '스몰 럭셔리(Small Luxury)',</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1d72a999-92d4-4334-9418-f4abc93290d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d16467c-5e2d-4a1f-bef4-a7953f11ab49\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">'다품종 소량 생산 파인 다이닝·디저트',</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f1453fa9-6731-45ee-9240-45cfca638a19\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4aea422-8072-4604-89b7-eec4e4241647\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">그리고 '크래프트 감성의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-57ea1ed8-0beb-4e8d-ac48-e7f8ce7e7167\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1fba97c9-da38-4566-8525-b42ce0462f98\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">프리미엄 브랜딩' 시장입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-77c872e3-7e43-4a56-b443-f614df02e4ff\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-90b5aa36-5721-45d8-810e-6365c1996a51\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6865093f-a2d3-42c2-ab86-89b0be847a43\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a24791e0-f432-40bd-8602-417c3c6a2f88\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요, 브랜드의 가치를 디자인하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-376f0466-d602-4fa4-948b-8f40c1116eea\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-15dd7d33-725e-4148-9475-ff07778c908d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지의 완성도를 높이는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-99930067-b47c-42e6-bcc8-b24eb408e2d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c504c58f-c21a-4a90-99fc-4072c280a803\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니((주)파파스컴퍼니)</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cf43fa37-6a6a-4e8d-a44e-a5666950faba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-067cb8e7-80fc-43ee-a7ce-f33feb2b8268\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-90a58ee4-186e-4548-93c4-28b9324d1ca7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-db93d0e0-6d0c-41ee-a570-df5358369203\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b96d7cf4-cd87-4b13-9ac0-45804f414597\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-258d489a-7a20-46d9-a43c-e90798bbe334\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-769d56e0-0e42-447b-a4a2-9726ca84b270\" style=\"color:#bb005c;\">\"저희는 수제 디저트 샵이라 스티커가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-778816f1-0d1d-4b7b-ae9a-1e11468c5291\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6eab8d4f-1679-4479-88a3-ae083f7e7a9c\" style=\"color:#bb005c;\">많이 필요 없는데, 꼭 평판(낱장) 스티커만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1811d56c-3a8f-42cc-9809-3e5cfe20f4ce\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a0c46a9f-15b5-4b3b-999c-158779033466\" style=\"color:#bb005c;\">써야 할까요?\"</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f9951a6d-05b2-4a92-9537-56a9eb71b066\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d053d26-9316-48d1-88e0-071c3f68c639\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0ceb8544-e35f-42bd-b71e-3450788e1ecc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-55efc047-8dfb-4063-b3a8-298016919cd0\" style=\"color:#bb005c;\">\"소규모로 프리미엄 미트(Meat) 브랜드를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4a5e046c-e295-4da6-a5f8-c0ba3ef5b6d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0df3210c-2d34-4efe-b63c-b5b3fdc5ddbd\" style=\"color:#bb005c;\">론칭하는데, 패키지에 고급스러운</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-76337e18-2e19-479e-96e8-eb874a577a02\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a708e613-38eb-42b7-af8e-d163eb127753\" style=\"color:#bb005c;\">롤스티커를 쓰고 싶어요. 가능할까요?\"</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2a1b3346-f61e-47c7-a813-a3371feced3e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c311d004-e5f5-4a19-bf23-e2f83d5d3a85\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f1b6454f-e556-46b8-b550-807d2dc7c6eb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-403ef703-b53c-4baa-be34-99d5cbdb3b4c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">최근 소규모 고부가가치 브랜드를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a2d1e3e9-ae7c-4675-9dc0-a237654bb99d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-37e518b5-41cb-40b1-b748-66d4af83b860\" style=\"color:#555555;\">운영하시는 대표님들께 가장 많이 받는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f8d550e5-99e3-44b6-afa2-faf81922cc2f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb5a3770-bd12-4360-85b5-ecc85e60aa8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">질문 중 하나입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f1796dbb-d989-4cbf-95d7-f514b596fd90\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-119f4981-4de6-48c3-9b72-07528a0e1db2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">흔히 '롤스티커(롤라벨)'라고 하면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-522f0872-5563-4f27-87dd-f4618bc2a51b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6d973ecb-0721-4709-b019-2273fae0e7cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대기업의 대량 생산 라인에서만 쓰는 것이라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-adfb5ac9-0f80-4237-b705-71eada2ee576\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c66651da-79ac-43a2-b13f-97f6e974dfbf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">생각하기 쉽지만, 최근 스몰 럭셔리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3def3060-0f9a-459c-80ac-a3fba1696903\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-64014827-7542-4419-ad0b-ed32374bbfa8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시장에서는 오히려 소량 롤스티커가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-96de49bb-42e5-4828-b1f3-9982f4305036\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-168db0dc-9ddc-41d1-b70a-ed27994e3e34\" style=\"color:#555555;\">브랜딩의 핵심 킥(Kick)으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7b5ce1e1-0509-49e9-b782-10e966a14e1a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c1d3e5c1-bd18-4b47-9f04-6ba7ea63e270\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자리 잡고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-45aa1ee9-c705-454f-91c8-d787e584d022\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eac167d8-63ff-47ef-8b00-35afd6d84b13\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-79cda0c0-61c7-45c7-8cd0-896a42cbbbc0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f52917ab-c9ec-4b6f-b396-92b4eb56dc6e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 대기업은 쉽게 흉내 낼 수 없는,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4d64d4bd-b27e-45d0-911d-536885c81755\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ec0a106-e334-4ca7-8072-f0cacb1cce12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오직 소규모 프리미엄 브랜드만을 위한</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ff53254f-eddc-4653-a83b-c741d311b919\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f7f33fa-5df6-4abb-9813-c69d59513dd9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">롤스티커 타깃 시장과 제품 전략을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d5135e03-3ede-4d0a-8db5-a6f252faab4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0bc0e145-7abf-471a-92fb-790983c168ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소개해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83e4fde4-da98-4530-9733-4f0d8aa681e4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224308480481/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-f9eba5e3-8e23-4bdf-9d08-6e6da5e1ea20\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98b5ac51-cdde-4343-a89a-74a3448984ed\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0258dacc-e27c-4cd8-b557-e64d79dc8e99\" style=\"\">고객님이 다음 업종에 종사하신다면 바로 문의주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eb7bef7a-9ce7-4868-9787-9cfb45e8e962\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-660198ac-41a6-41dc-a07f-1ee6263edca2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f3693c8-cf05-46d7-a530-693259f1c775\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 파인 다이닝 &amp; 프리미엄 수제 식음료 (F&amp;B)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75aaadb9-733d-4e4c-8c9b-42825a11ce51\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-10c730e9-93da-43a9-ab7b-fe74910983db\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주요 제품 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03e3f0c2-b038-44e3-a501-c4347cd94d57\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수제 프리미엄 소스, 고가형 핸드메이드 와인/전통주, 프리미엄 한우 유통 브랜드, 최고급 콜드브루 및 디저트.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9c5463cc-a26c-4dda-aaa8-5d480c8ccffe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224308480481/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-731e5732-8056-43c7-8d0e-0b3bc6986166\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224308480481/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6e1b311b-842e-412d-b463-88de7eec7622\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9da7ba85-ff11-42cc-bc1e-b3a0d741b922\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4dd57ac5-50d9-4704-9e98-d7f4dd0e525f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>전략 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7ea92fd-9581-4c29-b996-ba30e899446b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 시장의 핵심은 '갓 만들어진 신선함'과 '장인 정신'입니다. 낱장 스티커를 손으로 떼어 붙이다 보면 미세하게 삐뚤어지거나 지문이 묻어 고급스러운 맛이 떨어질 수 있습니다. 소형 수동/반자동 라벨러를 구비한 매장이나 소규모 가공 공장에서는 디지털 인쇄로 제작된 소량 롤스티커를 사용해 완벽한 정렬과 깔끔한 마무리를 구현, 시각적 신뢰도를 극대화합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3873f65-bfb9-4c4e-8c11-1b7529eabf1f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75592797-c2de-463e-9a74-b2cb1e41389f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b8dd9e4f-4c4a-407f-9294-6e1d0651c677\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5299e2fd-47a0-4c28-bf9c-b092d959556c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b9866be-8b69-441d-ba64-0697f85f7fd6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-662ec633-6fcc-4698-9573-d2341383b3f2\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 니치 향수 &amp; 비건 코스메틱 (Beauty)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9fcb9d8f-de5f-42e4-b6f3-89ed5ed6e508\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9fb26d59-cbe3-4d2e-ab5f-c2e50fb0d8f9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ea1c628f-d846-4016-abf3-8a7fa28d153a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주요 제품 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5d2a9130-6a87-41c1-8d59-aa40667bd94e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">커스텀 조향 향수, 소량 생산 비건 스킨케어, 핸드메이드 캔들 및 디퓨저.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5cb0311-5337-4095-9d46-88f2fbf08382\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb6e8c37-28eb-445d-a179-4c983b844cdd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a21888d3-0b6d-4418-95db-e1cbf2228b1d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f59219c2-28e7-4fd8-a7c4-99b9d9898dad\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>전략 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2576a6c-19f4-4da0-97df-92166071c470\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대형 브랜드의 대량 인쇄로는 표현하기 힘든 질감 중심의 특수 원단(예: 린넨, 머쉬룸, 350g 밍크지 계열의 얇은 버전 등)이나 금박·은박·디보싱(Debossing) 후가공을 더한 롤스티커 시장입니다. 용기 디자인이 미니멀할수록 라벨의 감촉과 박(Foil)의 퀄리티가 브랜드의 몸값을 결정합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-05771440-2af9-4d26-8d7b-d5a932645e82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:433px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224308480481/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0730893-9040-4f6c-9d85-1978b94a9361\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7b5fa1c-34bf-4c31-90f3-0af241430317\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-48f3e1db-93b6-4a18-9f1d-f58ccb124859\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44802666-c2ff-48b0-87be-b963d3117f3d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-48182f20-d2b9-4f2b-bb0d-383fc9c25104\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>· 고단가 웰니스 &amp; 라이프스타일 굿즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32ed2649-c3e9-4527-90e4-aa2bcb36e597\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f802da9d-58e0-42bf-abd9-9f9bb55b8474\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주요 제품 :</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc57f05d-434c-4283-9e83-211d52f04f89\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 프리미엄 영양제, 소규모 장인이 제작한 패브릭 미스트, 고급 주얼리 패키지.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-961bf585-405e-4bd9-96a0-e7b1ccba7dd8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa28e9fc-c3b8-46d5-8078-cef79b06d7bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3dc01069-fe55-4c76-b9e5-3d47dca29c66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8867ce11-d864-4b47-96dc-02939f0e6575\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>전략 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a3582249-bf43-400b-805d-25116a516a26\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다품종 소량 생산 방식으로 시즈널(Seasonal) 에디션을 자주 선보이는 브랜드에 적합합니다. 디지털 롤 인쇄 방식을 활용하면, 동판 가격 부담 없이 시즌별로 라벨 디자인을 유연하게 변경하면서도 '롤' 형태가 주는 깔끔한 보관성과 기성품 같은 완성도를 동시에 가져갈 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d24e6ad3-bc99-4582-8325-56b8e2975ee4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224308480481/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224308480481#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
